	(text "Notes related to TP4054-42-SOT25-R:\n1. It's recommended VCC range is: (4.0~9.0)V\n2. For the Programming Charge Current I(Bat) \n   there are two equations:\n	When I(Bat)≤0.15A, then:\n		I(Bat) = 1000/Rprog = 100mA\n	When I(Bat)>0.15A, then:\n		Rprog = 1000/I(Bat)*(1.2-4/3*I(Bat))"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 20.32 104.14 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1 1)
				(bold yes)
